comment: Lopez (BKN) makes contact with Holiday's (NOP) arm that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Cunningham (NOP) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Young (BKN) and does not affect his RSBQ.
Lopez (BKN) makes incidental contact with Gee (NOP) before the inbound pass.
Robinson (BKN) legally contests Holiday's (NOP) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release of the shot is considered incidental.
